<HEADLINE>
<P>
AFARIAN WILL PLAY 2 SPORTS AT SANTA CLARA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Chris Afarian, who graduated from Notre Dame High in June, will attend Santa 
Clara in the fall and play football and soccer on a partial athletic 
scholarship. 
</P>
<P>
Afarian, an All-San Fernando Valley League selection in both sports, converted 
all eight of his field-goal attempts for the Knights' football team and 
connected on each of his 53 extra-point attempts. 
</P>
<P>
Santa Clara competes in NCAA Division I in soccer, Division II in football. 
</P>
</TEXT>
