59 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: FESTIVAL NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GREG BRAXTON, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news servicesand the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Festival Club Introduced: The Open Festival on Tuesday reintroduced Los 
Angeles's arts community to Bruno's Ristorante, the former Westside hot spot 
that will be reopened during September's L.A. Festival as a meeting place for 
local and international artists. The "Festival Club" will feature informal 
performances by festival artists.GREG BRAXTON 
</P>
