LIMITATION); CALIFORNIA -- POLITICS; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; 
GOVERNMENT REFORM; INITIATIVES -- CALIFORNIA; PROPOSITION 131 (INCUMBENCY 
