<P>
A previously unknown faction calling itself the Palestine Revolutionary Squads 
said it will release two Swiss hostages of the International Committee of the 
Red Cross within 24 hours. The statement, handwritten in Arabic, was delivered 
to the independent Beirut newspaper An Nahar along with a photograph of Swiss 
captive Emmanuel Christen, 32. He and the other hostage, Elio Erriquez, 23, 
were kidnaped Oct. 6, 1989, in Sidon. 
